Archive: Multiple files into one archive file
Compress: Compress files lowering the total amount of memory by clever algorthims
.tar is the archive from the old tape archive
.gz gzip is for the compression
tar -zcvf docs.tar.gz Documents/
-f : filename
-v verbose
c : create new archive
z : g zip (compress the archive)
tar -zxf docs.tar.gz :  extract

